dct_title_s: [Christian Orthodox churches in part of Europe and the Middle East] [cartographic material].
dct_description_sm: "Copyright 1928 by George Stewart, Ph.D., F.R.G.S." Note in Constantinople: "The Orthodox Oecumenical Council composed of representative of Orthodox churches throughout the world. The Orthodox Church acceps the decisions of the first Seven Councils." Map shows centers of influence of Christian organizations in southern Europe and the Middle East, Map shows areas of British and French mandates. "This map is necessarily tentative".
